data.description: Charming 3-bedroom 2-bathroom home nestled right in the heart of Crestview on two lots, ready for you to make it home! A new roof was installed 3 years ago. The home features a spacious living area, with a wonderful galley style kitchen with tile in the kitchen, dining, laundry, and baths, with carpet in the master and guest room. A new hurricane sliding backdoor was installed in 2020. The backyard is large enough for a pool, swing set, trampoline, or even a she-shed!
